<keyLead id="EA06772E5F69A908FF75D0982CF1FA63" pageId="3" pageNumber="250">
2. Homogamous spikelet absent at the base of raceme; lower glume of sessile spikelet bimucronate.................................................... ..................................................................................................................................................... 
