<keyLead id="EA06772E5F69A908FF75D0DE2CF1F9A9" pageId="3" pageNumber="250">
3. Upper glume of the sessile spikelet bi-lobed, arista from sinus; lower floret entirely absent; lower glume of pedicelled spikelet longitudinally grooved; callus of pedicelled spikelet stipe-like, ca. 
<quantity id="960F79FE5F69A908FCAED3232AD1F9A8" box="[851,906,1549,1570]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="3" pageNumber="250" unit="mm" value="2.0">2 mm</quantity>
